node.title: Fruity Themes
node.excerpt: Adds different fruity color themes to select inside the settings window

node.title: More Presets
node.excerpt: Adds a new crop, pickaxe and axe preset. Presets in this plugin require Minecraft beta 1.16.100.56+

node.title: Recipe Snippets
node.excerpt: Adds better templates for custom recipes

node.title: Volcanic and Aquatic Themes
node.excerpt: Adds two new volcanic and aquatic color themes to select inside the settings window

node.title: Deep Blue Theme
node.excerpt: Adds a deep blue color theme to select inside the settings window

node.title: Lime Theme
node.excerpt: Adds a lime color theme to select inside the settings window

node.title: Black and White Theme
node.excerpt: Adds a black and white theme to select inside the settings window

node.title: Simple Block Rotation
node.excerpt: Adding rotation to blocks is as easy as it should be: Adding a single component!

node.title: More Vanilla Entity Presets
node.excerpt: Adds a cod, salmon and bat preset.

node.title: Json Encoder
node.excerpt: Encodes your json files into utf-16.

node.title: Item Equipped Sensor
node.excerpt: Adds a custom item component to allow you to simply run events and commands when the item is equipped/unequipped.

node.title: Custom Entity Syntax
node.excerpt: Adds support for custom entity syntax such as adding component groups or spell effects directly in events.
